oy Hattersley 2012 cropped 2.jpg|50px]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| rowspan=\"3\"|[[Labour Party (UK)|Labour]]<br />''([[Shadow Cabinet of Neil Kinnock|Kinnock]]'')\n| rowspan=\"3\"|[[Neil Kinnock]]<br /><small>2 October 1983&nbsp;\u2013<br />18 July 1992</small>\n| rowspan=\"3\"|[[File:Kinnock, Neil.jpg|50px]]\n| [[Roy Hattersley]]<br /><small>9 June 1983&nbsp;\u2013<br />11 June 1987</small>\n| [[File:Roy Hattersley 2012 cropped 2.jpg|50px]]\n| [[Gerald Kaufman]]<br /><small>2 October 1983&nbsp;\u2013<br />13 June 1987</small>\n| [[File:Kaufman.JPG|50px]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[John Smith (Labour Party leader)|John Smith]]<br /><small>11 June 1987&nbsp;\u2013<br />18 July 1992</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\"|\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Gerald Kaufman]]<br /><small>11 June 1987&nbsp;\u2013<br />19 July 1992</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[File:Kaufman.JPG|50px]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Roy Hattersley]]<br /><small>13 June 1987&nbsp;\u2013<br />19 July 1992</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[File:Roy Hattersley 2012 cropped 2.jpg|50px]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color: {{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| rowspan=\"4\"|[[Conservative Party (UK)|Conservative]]<br />''([[Major ministry (disambiguation)|Major]]''<!--intentional link to DAB page-->)\n|-\n! style=\"background-color: {{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |\n| [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour]]<br />''([[Shadow Cabinet of John Smith|Smith]]'')\n| [[John Smith (Labour Party leader)|John Smith]]<br /><small>18 July 1992&nbsp;\u2013<br />12 May 1994\u2020</small>\n| \n| rowspan=\"3\"|[[Gordon Brown]]<br /><small>18 July 1992&nbsp;\u2013<br />2 May 1997</small>\n| rowspan=\"3\"|[[File:Gordon Brown official.jpg|50px]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Jack Cunningham]]<br /><small>11 April 1992&nbsp;\u2013<br />22 July 1994</small>\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[File:No image.svg|50px]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Tony Blair]]<br /><small>19 July 1992&nbsp;\u2013<br />22 July 1994</small>\n| r